Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.37,0:00:37.11,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fsp0}This is a fate that brought us here watch my long shot
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.88,0:00:47.53,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fsp0}Feel like I am falling into the flame of lies
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.53,0:00:50.23,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fsp0}Tell me what do you want from me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.92,0:00:54.61,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fsp0}Trying not to step back to where I used to belong
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:00:57.28,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fsp0}Looking for the escape from pain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.56,0:01:01.75,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fsp0}I will cross my fingers hoping not to be sacrificed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.75,0:01:05.28,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}約束したんだ君とその希望に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.28,0:01:09.05,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fsp0}Get in the raid Get ready for the time to come
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.05,0:01:12.61,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}浮かび上がるシルエット追いかけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.61,0:01:16.02,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fsp0}Drop down the reason why I'm standing here alone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.02,0:01:19.53,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fsp0}May be it's already too late to regain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.68,0:01:24.88,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}運命としてかかげた灯を失くさないで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.88,0:01:26.15,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fsp0}Ever again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.15,0:01:29.67,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fsp0}What if I could right my wrongs and save you from the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.67,0:01:39.17,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fsp0\fs55}It's not enough It's not enough for me to break the rule upon this world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.15,0:01:44.17,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fsp0}I will never gonna leave you never wanna lose you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.17,0:01:46.62,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fsp0}we'll make it in the end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.79,0:01:52.87,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fsp0}Not backing down for real I won't trace someone else's life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:55.20,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fsp0}I know who I am
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.37,0:00:37.11,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}命運帶我們走到了這裡 見識我的豪賭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.88,0:00:47.53,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}彷彿落入了謊言的烈火之中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.53,0:00:50.23,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}請告訴我 你想讓我怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.92,0:00:54.61,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}為了保護我所在的家園
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:00:57.28,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我尋找著逃脫苦難的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.56,0:01:01.75,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我握拳祈禱不會有人犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.75,0:01:05.28,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我保證過不會放棄你和希望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.28,0:01:09.05,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}做好準備 面對必將到來的侵襲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.05,0:01:12.61,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}追趕著腦海裡浮現的倩影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.61,0:01:16.02,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}捨棄掉孤獨戰鬥的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.02,0:01:19.53,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}想奪回一切也許為時已晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.68,0:01:24.88,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}但也不要遺失命運給你的燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.88,0:01:26.15,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}再也不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.15,0:01:29.67,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}如果我能改掉錯誤 救你於水火之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.67,0:01:39.17,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}那也不夠我去打破這個世界的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.15,0:01:44.17,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我不會再丟下你 不會再失去你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.17,0:01:46.62,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我們一定能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.79,0:01:52.87,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我決不後退 決不成為別人理想的模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:55.20,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我知道我該過怎樣的人生
